00:01:12.730 --> 00:01:17.110
There are three expressions of gravity that
scientists find useful. We're going to talk

00:01:17.110 --> 00:01:23.120
about all three of them today: gravity near
the earth's surface, Newton's universal law

00:01:23.120 --> 00:01:29.720
of gravity, and Einstein's gravitational field
equations, which are the core of general relativity.

00:01:29.720 --> 00:01:34.110
We'll be spending most of our time with the
